Package com.ames.uncover.impl Description

These classes may be cool to read about but please do not use them in your implementation directly, or at least avoid. They may change as the project evolves. For other packages, we will try to keep backward compatibility, use @deprecated, etc. Classes in this package may be altered much more freely.
